OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWhile still very warm,
OL,6,Ftemperatures will be a little lower
OL,7,Fthan on previous days. Further periods
OL,8,Fof sunshine will develop, perhaps hazy
OL,9,Fand eventually sparking scattered
OL,10,Fshowers.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with showers
OL,13,Fand an isolated rumble of thunder.
OL,14,FTemperatures remain warm overnight.
OL,15,FWinds southwesterly and light but
OL,16,Fbreezy along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
